trigonometric \u1ecdr\u1ee5: Ọrụ nke akụkụ egosipụtara dị ka oke nke ogologo akụkụ nke triangle nwere aka nri
inverse \u1ecdr\u1ee5: Ọrụ enwetara site n'ịkọwapụta mgbanwe dabere na otu ọrụ dị ka mgbanwe nọọrọ onwe ya nke ọzọ
cosecant: Ntugharị nke ọrụ sine, akọwara dị ka oke nke hypotenuse na akụkụ nke ọzọ nke triangle nwere aka nri.
ihe na-efe efe: Ntugharị nke ọrụ tangent, akọwara dị ka oke nke dị n'akụkụ akụkụ nke ọzọ nke triangle nwere aka nri.
njirimara trigonometric: Ha nhata gụnyere ọrụ trigonometric bụ eziokwu maka ụkpụrụ niile nke mgbanwe
iwu nke sines: N'ime triangle, oke nke ogologo akụkụ na sine nke akụkụ nke ọzọ na-adịgide adịgide
iwu nke cosines: N'ime triangle, square nke akụkụ hà nhata na nchikota nke akụkụ abụọ nke ọzọ na-ewepụ ugboro abụọ ngwaahịa nke akụkụ abụọ a na cosine nke akụkụ ahụ gụnyere.
nha radian: Ntụle nke akụkụ dị na radian, nke bụ oke ogologo nke arc na radius ya
angular \u1ecds\u1ecd: Ọnụego mgbanwe nke akụkụ n'ihe gbasara oge
ogologo arc: Ebe dị n'etiti isi ihe abụọ n'akụkụ akụkụ nke mgbanaka
ngalaba: Akụkụ nke okirikiri nke radis abụọ gbachiri na arc ha etinyere
trigonometric ruru: Oke nke ogologo akụkụ abụọ nke triangle ziri ezi
trigonometric nhata: Nhazi nke gụnyere otu ma ọ bụ ọtụtụ ọrụ trigonometric nke mgbanwe
